CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, reads: "An Education, And How!-- Fifth Avenue Students are pictured in one of the many stunt acts exhibited last Thursday night when the Physical Education Department held its annual show. The boys are doing a real act which would take most of the grownups years of education plus: These boys have won a number of sports awards." -- Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Young men from Fifth Avenue High School, wearing gymnastics costumes with dark trousers, suspenders, and light colored tank tops inscribed "F", performing on stage for the Physical Education Department annual show
